elb" style="border-color: #ee9189;"> <img class="img-circle" src="/upload/author/1/eefc220d8b9085ec4debdcf4d58157a0_400_400_1.jpg" alt="B频道 Channel B"/> </a> <p>B频道 Channel B</p> </div> <div class="swiper-slide avatar"> <a href="/sc/author/陳劍鍠" style="border-color: #79cea7;"> <img class="img-circle" src="/upload/author/2/354fa1298202880ba45ff280e29dbfde_400_400_1.jpg" alt="陈剑鍠教授"/> </a> <p>陈剑鍠教授</p> </div> <div class="swiper-slide avatar"> <a href="/sc/author/法忍法師" style="border-color: #9e98c8;"> <img class="img-circle" src="/upload/author/4/61ba6c00d2792f5df1f69715d14d7b80_400_400_1.jpg" alt="法忍法师"/> </a> <p>法忍法师</p> </div> <div class="swiper-slide avatar"> <a href="/sc/author/鄺民彬" style="border-color: #d4b08c;"> <img class="img-circle" src="/upload/author/8/2e7a5b608c5e11b46353caff6b803cd7_400_400_1.jpg" alt="邝民彬"/> </a> <p>邝民彬</p> </div> <div class="swiper-slide avatar"> <a href="/sc/author/衍空法師" style="border-color: #ee9189;"> <img class="img-circle" src="/upload/author/12/dc3778dd3e073b2c1991dd50c1ac3641_400_400_1.jpg" alt="衍空法师"/> </a> <p>衍空法师</p> </div> <div class="swiper-slide avatar"> <a href="/sc/author/gerald-lee" style="border-color: #79cea7;"> <img class="img-circle" src="/upload/author/16/5536fb4afe4826971172e18470483aa1_400_400_1.jpg" alt="Gerald Lee"/> </a> <p>Gerald Lee</p> </div> <div class="swiper-slide avatar"> <a href="/sc/author/衍陽法師" style="border-color: #9e98c8;"> <img class="img-circle" src="/upload/author/18/a858a19edb56e8b47a600dc9505d0606_400_400_1.jpg" alt="衍阳法师"/> </a> <p>衍阳法师</p> </div> <div class="swiper-slide avatar"> <a href="/sc/author/傳燈法師" style="border-color: #d4b08c;"> <img class="img-circle" src="/upload/author/22/e88172c9e81d59d85fee8d2a692732cd_400_400_1.jpg" alt="传灯法师"/> </a> <p>传灯法师</p> </div> <div class="swiper-slide avatar"> <a href="/sc/author/corrin-amp-helen" style="border-color: #ee9189;"> <img class="img-circle" src="/upload/author/24/0eaeb5f808cf2a6aa3fe8488be50cea7_400_400_1.jpg" alt="Corrin &amp; Helen"/> </a> <p